    <h3 class='center' style="font-size:20px;">These rehab projects were made possible due to the partnership between Sacramento Affordable Housing Organization and Sacramento Housing and Redevelopment Agency (<a href="http://www.shra.org/" target="_blank" style="color:#62c6d5;">SHRA</a>) under the federal Neighborhood Stabilization Program.</h3>
